'''''Lost Tales''''' is the second EP by [[Summoning]], released in [[2003]]. It consists of two songs, Arcenstone that was originally written for Silenus' Mirkwood project and Saruman, a left over from the [[Dol Guldur (album)|Dol Guldur]] sessions in [[1996]].
